    dc:description "FIGURES 28 – 37. Paranura reducta sp. nov.: 28, habitus and dorsal chaetotaxy (holotype); 29, chaetotaxy of labrum; 30, dorsal side of apical bulb; 31, dorsal chaetotaxy of ant. III – IV; 32, chaetotaxy of labium and group Vi; 33, apical part of labrum; 34, furca rudimentary; 35, ventral chaetotaxy of abdomen; 36, S-chaeta of abd. V; 37, chaeta Di 1 of abd. V." ;
