    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.236717>
    dc:description "FIGURES 58 – 69. Paranura kedrovayensis sp. nov.: 58, chaetotaxy of labium and group Vi; 60, habitus and dorsal chaetotaxy; 61, chaetotaxy of labrum; 62, dorsal side of apical bulb; 63, ventral side of apical bulb; 64, dorsal chaetotaxy of ant. III – IV; 66, chaetotaxy of trochanter, 67, ventral chaetotaxy of abdomen; 68, chaeta Di 1 of abd. V; 69, S-chaeta of abd. V; Paranura mjohjangensis: 59, chaetotaxy of labium; 65, chaetotaxy of trochanter." ;
